{"tid":1055480,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人睇左 Free Solo?","createTime":"2019-03-10T14:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T17:23:20.000Z","uid":66893,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4e6cc72d54ffd6cf3295f1a67a0686e99ffcde","tid":1055480,"uid":66893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:46:25.000Z","msg":"Free Solo係 National Geographic製作嘅documentary， 講述攀岩專家Alex Honnold徒手攀上Yosemite嘅El Capitan，成為史上第一人成功free solo呢個岩壁嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/9/9c/Free_Solo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F9%2F9c%2FFree_Solo.png&h=4ee4ec26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人認為好值得睇，好難想像係冇任何安全裝備下攀上咁高嘅山，即使再細嘅失誤已經可以粉身碎骨。睇之前可能覺得佢會靠好多經驗同直覺去爬，但睇完你會發覺佢對呢4個鐘嘅爬山路線嘅每一舊石、每一個凹位都牢牢記住。而且成個拍攝方法係成隊crew跟佢一齊爬，d鏡頭充分反映到係山上面果種驚心動魄。全片大概100分鐘，好值得睇。"},{"pid":"647c016994506dc3f091b1fc4040fdf1d0776a44","tid":1055480,"uid":238673,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:50:15.000Z","msg":"差點睇做 han solo <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ccab1132415a05acd18d05d27faadab4b2194d1","tid":1055480,"uid":187378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T14:56:10.000Z","msg":"睇到後面睇到手心都出汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944975637c124d0e8b4519eea50bb643033c8636","tid":1055480,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:15:35.000Z","msg":"其實拍得麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好鬆散，咩都講啲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a28b19649bab56669a563b2fd7fcb492eb890b","tid":1055480,"uid":66893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"944975637c124d0e8b4519eea50bb643033c8636","tid":1055480,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:15:35.000Z","msg":"其實拍得麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好鬆散，咩都講啲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:29:05.000Z","msg":"同意可以編排得更好，但基本上冇乜資料性可以講。加上最很free solo果陣為左唔影響佢發輝，冇左好多攝影師，感覺上比佢練習時少左好多精彩鏡頭可以用。<br />\n<br />\nBtw佢條女唔小心果到之後就到佢條女冇乜好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d1d86d056a37bc0f95185d224c57e85366af17","tid":1055480,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"鬼佬玩命就得"},{"pid":"fed0b7efcfbdda6136c8ed108a73cbaef0e172bf","tid":1055480,"uid":160051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"外面有IMAX睇<br />\n凝住會睇到標尿"},{"pid":"eb9e62df403e05435353d5ca3c9a40a98ef00baf","tid":1055480,"uid":60867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:35:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12594231e9d19dabfd3e5265bf8100560f622e23","tid":1055480,"uid":90315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:04:11.000Z","msg":"fox幾時上"},{"pid":"a7826b02a5cebeb0d2400eabc4922e906cfc0234","tid":1055480,"uid":66893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb9e62df403e05435353d5ca3c9a40a98ef00baf","tid":1055480,"uid":60867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T16:35:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T17:07:51.000Z","msg":"好似之前有"},{"pid":"eab46a90300611979737e06d9c471036eb9e60c9","tid":1055480,"uid":66893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7826b02a5cebeb0d2400eabc4922e906cfc0234","tid":1055480,"uid":66893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb9e62df403e05435353d5ca3c9a40a98ef00baf","tid":1055480,"uid":60867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019